## ▶️ How to Run the Project

1. Clone the repository
```
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Garbage-Classification-CV.git
```

2. Install required libraries
```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

3. Run the training script
```
python train.py
```

4. Test the model
```
python predict.py
```

